snippet.title: Tiny Bird Garden Deluxe Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Retro Duck is proud to announce - Tiny Bird Garden Deluxe for PC and Mac! Coming December 17th, 2018! Please help us spread the word - wishlist + preorders available now! :D

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/945440/Tiny_Bird_Garden_Deluxe/
